      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FLEETWOOD EROS (2) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (23.72) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to his credit. Worth another chance. CABAO LAPIS (1) was unfavoured last start but gave a huge sight when led for much of the way to place (23.41) at this track in a Grade 5 over 410m. Goes very well from this draw with two wins and two minor placings from five starts. Overdue and is among the main hopes. PAW MAUD (7) missed the frame last time when fifth (23.50) at this track but prior to that had two placings in a row. Form here sound including two wins. Comes through a solid form race last start. Likely to be thereabouts. PAW LAMPADES (5) cannot be overlooked following a recent top-three finish.",
